{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":197,"text":"I would like to talk to you about a story"},{"time":2082,"text":"about a small town kid."},{"time":4563,"text":"I don't know his name, but I do know his story."},{"time":8238,"text":"He lives in a small village in southern Somalia."},{"time":11314,"text":"His village is near Mogadishu."},{"time":15344,"text":"Drought drives the small village into poverty"},{"time":17518,"text":"and to the brink of starvation."},{"time":19386,"text":"With nothing left for him there,"},{"time":21222,"text":"he leaves for the big city,"},{"time":23049,"text":"in this case, Mogadishu, the capital of Somalia."},{"time":26454,"text":"When he arrives, there are no opportunities,"},{"time":29284,"text":"no jobs, no way forward."},{"time":32272,"text":"He ends up living in a tent city"},{"time":34296,"text":"on the outskirts of Mogadishu."},{"time":37000,"text":"Maybe a year passes, nothing."},{"time":41009,"text":"One day, he's approached by a gentleman"},{"time":43309,"text":"who offers to take him to lunch,"},{"time":45507,"text":"then to dinner, to breakfast."},{"time":48583,"text":"He meets this dynamic group of people,"},{"time":51602,"text":"and they give him a break."},{"time":53107,"text":"He's given a bit of money"},{"time":54426,"text":"to buy himself some new clothes,"},{"time":56528,"text":"money to send back home to his family."},{"time":59064,"text":"He is introduced to this young woman."},{"time":61037,"text":"He eventually gets married."},{"time":62752,"text":"He starts this new life."},{"time":65557,"text":"He has a purpose in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68483,"text":"One beautiful day in Mogadishu,"},{"time":71257,"text":"under an azure blue sky,"},{"time":74145,"text":"a car bomb goes off."},{"time":76666,"text":"That small town kid with the big city dreams"},{"time":79861,"text":"was the suicide bomber,"},{"time":82109,"text":"and that dynamic group of people"},{"time":84467,"text":"were al Shabaab, a terrorist organization"},{"time":86836,"text":"linked to al Qaeda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90517,"text":"So how does the story of a small town kid"},{"time":93389,"text":"just trying to make it big in the city"},{"time":95210,"text":"end up with him blowing himself up?"},{"time":98040,"text":"He was waiting."},{"time":100012,"text":"He was waiting for an opportunity,"},{"time":101910,"text":"waiting to begin his future,"},{"time":103692,"text":"waiting for a way forward,"},{"time":105727,"text":"and this was the first thing that came along."},{"time":108106,"text":"This was the first thing that pulled him out"},{"time":110520,"text":"of what we call waithood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113460,"text":"And his story repeats itself"},{"time":115756,"text":"in urban centers around the world."},{"time":118172,"text":"It is the story of the disenfranchised,"},{"time":120926,"text":"unemployed urban youth"},{"time":122734,"text":"who sparks riots in Johannesburg,"},{"time":126677,"text":"sparks riots in London,"},{"time":129011,"text":"who reaches out for something other than waithood."},{"time":133665,"text":"For young people, the promise of the city,"},{"time":136329,"text":"the big city dream is that of opportunity,"},{"time":139023,"text":"of jobs, of wealth,"},{"time":141178,"text":"but young people are not sharing\nin the prosperity of their cities."},{"time":144919,"text":"Often it's youth who suffer from\nthe highest unemployment rates."},{"time":149017,"text":"By 2030, three out of five people living in cities"},{"time":152210,"text":"will be under the age of 18."},{"time":154770,"text":"If we do not include young people"},{"time":156534,"text":"in the growth of our cities,"},{"time":158353,"text":"if we do not provide them opportunities,"},{"time":160832,"text":"the story of waithood,"},{"time":162854,"text":"the gateway to terrorism, to violence, to gangs,"},{"time":165767,"text":"will be the story of cities 2.0."},{"time":169942,"text":"And in my city of birth, Mogadishu,"},{"time":173103,"text":"70 percent of young people\nsuffer from unemployment."},{"time":176793,"text":"70 percent don't work,"},{"time":179171,"text":"don't go to school."},{"time":181198,"text":"They pretty much do nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183623,"text":"I went back to Mogadishu last month,"},{"time":187139,"text":"and I went to visit Madina Hospital,"},{"time":189149,"text":"the hospital I was born in."},{"time":191197,"text":"I remember standing in front of that"},{"time":193222,"text":"bullet-ridden hospital thinking,"},{"time":196200,"text":"what if I had never left?"},{"time":198233,"text":"What if I had been forced"},{"time":199426,"text":"into that same state of waithood?"},{"time":201945,"text":"Would I have become a terrorist?"},{"time":205956,"text":"I'm not really sure about the answer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208847,"text":"My reason for being in Mogadishu that month"},{"time":211015,"text":"was actually to host"},{"time":212562,"text":"a youth leadership and entrepreneurship summit."},{"time":215109,"text":"I brought together about 90 young Somali leaders."},{"time":218105,"text":"We sat down and brainstormed on solutions"},{"time":220351,"text":"to the biggest challenges facing their city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223227,"text":"One of the young men in the room was Aden."},{"time":226629,"text":"He went to university in Mogadishu, graduated."},{"time":231084,"text":"There were no jobs, no opportunities."},{"time":233273,"text":"I remember him telling me,"},{"time":234991,"text":"because he was a college graduate,"},{"time":237799,"text":"unemployed, frustrated,"},{"time":240549,"text":"that he was the perfect target for al Shabaab"},{"time":242946,"text":"and other terrorist organizations, to be recruited."},{"time":245998,"text":"They sought people like him out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249876,"text":"But his story takes a different route."},{"time":252972,"text":"In Mogadishu, the biggest barrier"},{"time":254909,"text":"to getting from point A to point B are the roads."},{"time":258162,"text":"Twenty-three years of civil war"},{"time":259945,"text":"have completely destroyed the road system,"},{"time":262176,"text":"and a motorbike can be the easiest way"},{"time":264185,"text":"to get around."},{"time":265815,"text":"Aden saw an opportunity and seized it."},{"time":269056,"text":"He started a motorbike company."},{"time":271181,"text":"He began renting out motorbikes"},{"time":273472,"text":"to local residents who couldn't normally afford them."},{"time":276772,"text":"He bought 10 bikes, with the help"},{"time":278793,"text":"of family and friends,"},{"time":280491,"text":"and his dream is to eventually expand"},{"time":282224,"text":"to several hundred within the next three years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285205,"text":"How is this story different?"},{"time":287773,"text":"What makes his story different?"},{"time":290130,"text":"I believe it is his ability to identify"},{"time":292960,"text":"and seize a new opportunity."},{"time":296298,"text":"It's entrepreneurship,"},{"time":298329,"text":"and I believe entrepreneurship can be"},{"time":300088,"text":"the most powerful tool against waithood."},{"time":303066,"text":"It empowers young people"},{"time":304836,"text":"to be the creators of the very economic opportunities"},{"time":308216,"text":"they are so desperately seeking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310714,"text":"And you can train young people to be entrepreneurs."},{"time":314396,"text":"I want to talk to you about a young man"},{"time":316512,"text":"who attended one of my meetings,"},{"time":318801,"text":"Mohamed Mohamoud, a florist."},{"time":321685,"text":"He was helping me train some of the young people"},{"time":323368,"text":"at the summit in entrepreneurship"},{"time":324805,"text":"and how to be innovative"},{"time":326427,"text":"and how to create a culture of entrepreneurship."},{"time":329194,"text":"He's actually the first florist Mogadishu has seen"},{"time":331691,"text":"in over 22 years,"},{"time":334375,"text":"and until recently, until Mohamed came along,"},{"time":337639,"text":"if you wanted flowers at your wedding,"},{"time":339529,"text":"you used plastic bouquets"},{"time":340922,"text":"shipped from abroad."},{"time":342508,"text":"If you asked someone,"},{"time":344314,"text":"\"When was the last time you saw fresh flowers?\""},{"time":346589,"text":"for many who grew up under civil war,"},{"time":349175,"text":"the answer would be, \"Never.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":351958,"text":"So Mohamed saw an opportunity."},{"time":353906,"text":"He started a landscaping and design floral company."},{"time":358353,"text":"He created a farm right outside of Mogadishu,"},{"time":361661,"text":"and started growing tulips and lilies,"},{"time":363717,"text":"which he said could survive"},{"time":365423,"text":"the harsh Mogadishu climate."},{"time":368134,"text":"And he began delivering flowers to weddings,"},{"time":371832,"text":"creating gardens at homes"},{"time":373765,"text":"and businesses around the city,"},{"time":376369,"text":"and he's now working on creating"},{"time":378106,"text":"Mogadishu's first public park in 22 years."},{"time":381731,"text":"There's no public park in Mogadishu."},{"time":383830,"text":"He wants to create a space where families,"},{"time":386159,"text":"young people, can come together,"},{"time":387810,"text":"and, as he says, smell the proverbial roses."},{"time":392448,"text":"And he doesn't grow roses because"},{"time":394404,"text":"they use too much water, by the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398528,"text":"So the first step is to inspire young people,"},{"time":402840,"text":"and in that room, Mohamed's presence"},{"time":405032,"text":"had a really profound impact\non the youth in that room."},{"time":408508,"text":"They had never really thought\nabout starting up a business."},{"time":411095,"text":"They've thought about working for an NGO,"},{"time":412942,"text":"working for the government,"},{"time":414629,"text":"but his story, his innovation,"},{"time":418936,"text":"really had a strong impact on them."},{"time":420889,"text":"He forced them to look at their city"},{"time":423008,"text":"as a place of opportunity."},{"time":424762,"text":"He empowered them to believe\nthat they could be entrepreneurs,"},{"time":428510,"text":"that they could be change makers."},{"time":430930,"text":"By the end of the day, they were coming up"},{"time":432490,"text":"with innovative solutions"},{"time":434041,"text":"to some of the biggest challenges facing their city."},{"time":437373,"text":"They came up with entrepreneurial solutions"},{"time":439976,"text":"to local problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442898,"text":"So inspiring young people"},{"time":445129,"text":"and creating a culture of entrepreneurship"},{"time":447543,"text":"is a really great step,"},{"time":449410,"text":"but young people need capital"},{"time":451099,"text":"to make their ideas a reality."},{"time":452888,"text":"They need expertise and mentorship"},{"time":455212,"text":"to guide them in developing\nand launching their businesses."},{"time":458612,"text":"Connect young people with the resources they need,"},{"time":461099,"text":"provide them the support they need\nto go from ideation to creation,"},{"time":464564,"text":"and you will create catalysts for urban growth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468664,"text":"For me, entrepreneurship is more than just"},{"time":471588,"text":"starting up a business."},{"time":473144,"text":"It's about creating a social impact."},{"time":475525,"text":"Mohamed is not simply selling flowers."},{"time":477660,"text":"I believe he is selling hope."},{"time":480147,"text":"His Peace Park, and that's what he calls it,"},{"time":482736,"text":"when it's created, will actually transform"},{"time":484908,"text":"the way people see their city."},{"time":486980,"text":"Aden hired street kids to help rent out"},{"time":489133,"text":"and maintain those bikes for him."},{"time":490995,"text":"He gave them the opportunity to escape"},{"time":493053,"text":"the paralysis of waithood."},{"time":495989,"text":"These young entrepreneurs are having"},{"time":498019,"text":"a tremendous impact in their cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501553,"text":"So my suggestion is,"},{"time":504069,"text":"turn youth into entrepreneurs,"},{"time":506585,"text":"incubate and nurture their inherent innovation,"},{"time":509808,"text":"and you will have more stories\nof flowers and Peace Parks"},{"time":513647,"text":"than of car bombs and waithood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":516740,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":519560,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}